{
  "texts": [
    "These types of behavior are confirmed in the experiment (Figs.",
    "2c, d and S5 and Supplementary Videos 4-7).",
    "The motions of CAPs are quantified by mean square displacement (MSD) hjΔrj 2 i.",
    "We find that MSD ∝ t 2 (i.e., ballistic) at short times and ∝t (i.e., diffusive) at long times (Fig. 3).",
    "The result is in accordance with our expectation that a CAP moves ballistically at t ≪ τ p and diffuses randomly at t ≫ τ p because it orbits many cycles during a long time step."
  ]
}